node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.

node.text: Founded by Jeff Bezos, space travel company Blue Origin completed its first passenger flight on July 20. The rocket, named New Shepard, carried Bezos and three other passengers more than 65-miles above Earth, just to the boundary of space, known as the Kármán line. Watch our latest episode of HBNN to learn more.

node.title: @jeffbezos Completes His First Flight into Space

@hypebeastcarclub: The 1998 @mercedesbenz AMG CLK GTR Strassenversion is officially up for auction via @goodingandcompany. The car comes with a mid-mounted 6.9-liter V12 engine that produces 604 horsepower and also features a paddle-shifted 6-speed Xtrac sequential transaxle. Find out more details via the link in bio. Gooding & Company expects the car to auction between $8.5 million to $10 million USD. ⁠⁠
Photo: Josh Hway

@hypebeastwatches: @fpjourneofficial has revealed a collaborative prototype watch with Francis Ford Coppola for @onlywatch_official. Key to the design is an automaton with different fingers that appear and disappear to indicate the hour. Other details include Tantalum and 18K rose gold, commemorative engraving, 396 components, and an orange alligator strap. Learn more via the link in bio.⁠
Photo: F.P.Journe

@hypebeastmusic: As the week in music comes to a close, we’ve rounded up some of the best new tracks and projects. Our favorites include @isaiahrashad, @iamdoechii, @kalbanx, @santandave, @thareal_smiley, @champagnepapi, @leonbridgesofficial, @sammhenshaw, and many more. #hypeAF: Icelandic designer @sruli_recht has designed a number of innovative shoes to combat harsh weather conditions. The Damage capsule collection features “shoes for a post-traumatic future,” and consists of three unique concepts tackling everything from extreme flooding to intense heat. Learn more about each shoe via the link in bio. The concept will not be manufactured, but rather, sold as digital art NFTs.⁠⁠

node.text:
#hypeAF: French designer Thierry Gaugain has unveiled the "G-Train", a $350 million private 1,300 foot smart train that reminds us of the "Snow Piercer". It comprises 14 sleek cars that feature a state-of-the-art glass exterior that can change colors and transparency depending on the environment. Additionally, the train will come with an owners suite, nearly 20 guest rooms, gym, spa and a range of luxurious offerings. The "G-Train" is currently still in its conceptual stages. ⁠⁠
Photo: Thierry Gaugain

node.text: The new album is named for West’s late mother, who passed away in 2007. While DONDA explores a wider range of genres than his previous album Jesus is King, it features some of the religious themes that West has pivoted to in his recent music. A partial tracklist posted by West ahead of the release listed titles like “Pure Souls” and “Keep My Spirit Alive.” The album will be available for purchase and streaming on July 23rd.
